3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EFaridabad%20Police%20has%20urged%20citizens%20to%20not%20click%20on%20any%20links%20they%20receive%20in%20the%20name%20of%20e-challan.%20The%20authorities%20added%20that%20fraudsters%20can%20hack%20into%20your%20bank%20account%20with%20just%20one%20click%20on%20these%20fake%20links.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20you%20receive%20a%20link%20for%20a%20traffic%20challan%2C%20don't%20click%20these%20links.%20By%20clicking%20upon%20these%20links%20for%20payment%2C%20fraudsters%20can%20hack%20your%20bank%20account%2C%E2%80%9D%20read%20the%20text%20attached%20to%20an%20infographic.%20The%20police%20have%20also%20differentiated%20between%20the%20original%20link%20of%20the%20e-challan%20and%20the%20fake%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9CCyber%20frauds%20are%20now%20making%20people%20their%20victims%20by%20using%20the%20growing%20trend%20of%20e-challan%20payment%20as%20a%20weapon%2C%E2%80%9D%20DCP%20Hemendra%20Kumar%20Meena%20was%20quoted%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EUrging%20citizens%20to%20not%20click%20any%20type%20of%20links%20they%20receive%20through%20a%20text%20message%2C%20DCP%20Meena%20informed%20that%20the%20fraud%20messages%20are%20created%20in%20such%20a%20manner%20that%20it%20will%20conclude%20with%20a%20link.%20%E2%80%9CYou%20have%20been%20issued%20a%20challan.%20You%20can%20pay%20your%20fine%20by%20clicking%20on%20this%20link%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20authorities%20notified%20citizens%20about%20how%20they%20could%20differentiate%20between%20the%20original%20and%20the%20fake%20message.%20The%20statement%20informed%20that%20an%20original%20challan%20message%20will%20include%20%E2%80%9Cengine%20number%2C%20vehicle%20identification%20number%20(VIN)%20and%20other%20information%20about%20your%20vehicle.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EIn%20addition%2C%20the%20official%20challan%20message%20will%20end%20with%20a%20government%20link%3A%C2%A0%3Ca%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fechallan.parivahan.gov.in%2F%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1693457256894000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw1WpxXz3SWLkZrDAUtTOTWQ%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fechallan.parivahan.gov.in%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Fechallan.parivahan.%3Cwbr%3Egov.in%2F%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EHowever%2C%20the%20fake%20messages%20are%20being%20concluded%20with%20a%20link%20that%20doesn't%20include%20.%3Ca%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttp%3A%2F%2Fgov.in%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1693457256894000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw0bmnZJX-e_7kCZLXFJ6oez%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fgov.in%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egov.in%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0at%20the%20end.%20The%20fake%20e-challan%20message%20will%20have%20links%20like%C2%A0%3Ca%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fechallan.parivahan.in%2F%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1693457256894000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw3i9j_KXyIjKtdHM--Sn9xW%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fechallan.parivahan.in%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Fechallan.parivahan.in%2F%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cwbr%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EFaridabad%20police%20added%20that%20as%20soon%20as%20any%20vehicle%20owner%20clicks%20on%20the%20link%20and%20enters%20bank%20account%20number%20and%20card%20details%2C%20fraudsters%20first%20hack%20the%20person's%20phone%20and%20after%20some%20time%20they%20clear%20out%20the%20entire%20balance%20available%20in%20the%20account.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EPolice%20spokesperson%20Sube%20Singh%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CIf%20you%20have%20been%20a%20victim%20of%20any%20online%20fraud%2C%20immediately%20call%20the%20National%20Cyber%20Complaint%20Portal%20number%201930%20and%20regis