%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F103200126.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3ESGPC%20filed%20a%20complaint%20against%20the%20makers%20of%20'Yaariyan%202%E2%80%99%20for%20hurting%20Sikh%20sentiments%20with%20the%20Amritsar%20police%20commissioner%20on%20Tuesday.%20However%2C%20the%20filmmaker%20of%20'Yaariyan%202%E2%80%99%20claimed%20the%20actor%20is%20wearing%20a%20%E2%80%98khukri%E2%80%99%20and%20not%20a%20%E2%80%98kirpan%E2%80%99%20and%20that%20they%20have%20no%20intention%20to%20offend%20or%20disrespect%20any%20religious%20beliefs.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fsgpc-files-complaint-against-the-makers-of-yaariyan-2-for-hurting-sikh-sentiments%2Farticleshow%2F103200126.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20Is%20Cracking%20Down%20On%20Teachers%20Using%20Phones%20During%20Class%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ENoting%20that%20the%20use%20of%20cellphones%20by%20teachers%20inside%20the%20classroom%20distracts%20students%20and%20teachers%2C%20diverting%20them%20from%20learning%2C%20the%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20government%20has%20banned%20the%20use%20of%20mobile%20phones%20in%20classrooms.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20decision%20was%20taken%20at%20a%20meeting%20chaired%20by%20state%20Education%20Minister%20Botcha%20Satyanarayana%20earlier%20this%20month%2C%20where%20the%20consensus%20among%20teachers%2C%20union%20representatives%20and%20education%20experts%20was%20to%20restrict%20the%20use%20of%20phones%20in%20the%20classrooms%20as%20%26quot%3Btheir%20negative%20impact%20outweighs%20their%20utility%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20state%20government%20cited%20the%20Global%20Educational%20Monitoring%20Report%2C%202023%2C%20by%20UNESCO%20and%20said%20that%20even%20when%20they%20are%20not%20actively%20using%20their%20phones%2C%20students%20encounter%20difficulty%20in%20maintaining%20concentration%20when%20studying%20in%20close%20proximity%20to%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20statement%20by%20the%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20government%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIt%20has%20been%20seen%20that%20many%20teachers%20take%20mobile%20phones%20into%20the%20classrooms%20during%20teaching%20hours%20for%20their%20personal%20use%20and%20not%20for%20any%20professional%20requirement.%20This%20diverts%20teaching%20time%20in%20the%20classroom%20to%20other%20purposes%20that%20are%20unproductive%20for%20the%20academic%20improvement%20of%20children.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETeachers%20will%20be%20required%20to%20deposit%20their%20mobile%20phones%2C%20set%20to%20silent%20mode%2C%20with%20the%20headmaster%20immediately%20after%20marking%20their%20attendance.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20also%20laid%20out%20the%20punishment%20for%20teachers%20if%20they%20are%20caught%20using%20phones%20in%20classrooms.%20For%20the%20first%20offence%2C%20the%20teacher's%20mobile%20phone%20will%20be%20confiscated%20by%20the%20headmaster%20or%20inspection%20officer%20and%20kept%20in%20the%20main%20office%20until%20the%20end%20of%20the%20school%20day.%20Before%20being%20allowed%20to%20take%20the%20phone%2C%20the%20teacher%20will%20have%20to%20give%20an%20undertaking%20to%20not%20repeat%20the%20offence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20second%20offence%2C%20the%20teacher's%20mobile%20phone%20will%20be%20confiscated%20and%20held%20in%20the%20main%20office%20until%20the%20end%20of%20the%20school%20day.%20The%20Mandal%20Education%20Officer%20(MEO)%20will%20be%20contacted%20and%20informed%20of%20the%20teacher's%20refusal%20to%20follow%20the%20mobile%20phone%20policy.%20The%20teacher%20can%20pick%20up%20their%20phones%20after%20a%20discussion%20with%20the%20MEO%20and%20after%20being%20issued%20a%20warning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20third-time%20offenders%2C%20the%20phone%20will%20be%20confiscated%20and%20sent%20to%20the%20District%20Education%20Officer.%20The%20teacher%20will%20be%20given%20back%20the%20phone%20only%20after%20a%20discussion%20with%20the%20DEO%20and%20after%20the%20offence%20is%20recorded%20in%20their%20service%20book.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20statement%20said%20headmasters%20have%20been%20asked%20to%20ensure%20vigilant%20supervision%20and%20adherence%20to%20the%20directives%20and%20any%20deviations%20must%20be%20%26quot%3Bmeticulously%20documented%20and%20communicated%20to%20inspecting%20authorities%20for%20action%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20violations%20are%20noticed%2C%20inspecting%20officers%2C%20whether%20on%20regular%20inspection%20or%20surprise%20inspections%2C%20can%20propose%20action%20against%20the%20head%20of%20the%20school.%20The%20headmaster%20will%20also%20be%20held%20accountable%20if%20complaints%20are%20received%20from%20students%20or%20the%20general%20public.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20state%20government%20has%20asked%20District%20Education%20Officers%20to%20conduct%20awareness%20meetings%20and%20workshops%20with%20teachers%20to%20help%20in%20the%20smooth%20implementation%20of%20the%20directives.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCollective%20attempts%20can%20forge%20an%20educational%20environment%20that%20harnesses%20the%20positive%20attributes%20of%20technology%20while%20safeguarding%20the%20well-being%20of%20students%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20August%2010%2C%20the%20Delhi%20Directorate%20of%20Education%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Feducation%2Fdelhi-students-barred-from-using-mobiles-in-classrooms-4287920%5C%22%3Ehad%20also%20banned%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20use%20of%20mobile%20phones%20in%20classrooms%20in%20both%20government%20schools%20and%20private%20schools.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETeachers%20had%20also%20been%20asked%20to%20avoid%20using%20phones%20in%20places%20like%20classrooms%2C%20playgrounds%2C%20laboratories%20and%20libraries%20where%20teaching%20and%20learning%20activities%20take%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693377540000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2020-01%2Fifm6g8vs_mobile-generic-istock-650_625x300_31_January_20.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fusing-phones-in-class-will-now-earn-andhra-pradesh-teachers-a-call-from-headmaster-4341502%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Noting%20that%20the%20use%20of%20cellphones%20by%20teachers%20inside%20the%20classroom%20distracts%20students%20and%20teachers%2C%20diverting%20them%20from%20learning%2C%20the%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20government%20has%20banned%20the%20use%20of%20mobile%20phones%20in%20classrooms.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fusing-phones-in-class-will-now-earn-andhra-pradesh-teachers-a-call-from-headmaster-4341502%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fusing-phones-in-class-will-now-earn-andhra-pradesh-teachers-a-call-from-headmaster-4341502%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fusing-phones-in-class-will-now-earn-andhra-pradesh-teachers-a-call-from-headmaster-4341502%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Adarsh%20joins%20Alien%20prequel%20series%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693377492000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-103200127%2Cimgsize-18856.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fadarsh-gourav-to-feature-in-ridley-scotts-alien-prequel-series%2Farticleshow%2F103200225.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F103200225.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EAdarsh%20Gourav%20who%20was%20last%20seen%20in%20Guns%20and%20Gulaabs%20will%20be%20seen%20in%20Ridley%20Scott's%20Alien.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%