that%20all%20the%20neighbouring%20countries%20are%20%26quot%3Bnot%20friendly%26quot%3B%20and%20there%20is%20a%20need%20to%20mainstream%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20in%20view%20of%20its%20history%20and%20current%20situation%20--%20%26quot%3Bstone%20pelting%2C%20strikes%2C%20deaths%20and%20terror%20attacks%26quot%3B%20--%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20weighed%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOnce%20you%20concede%20that%20power%20to%20the%20Union%20in%20relation%20to%20every%20Indian%20state%2C%20how%20do%20you%20ensure%20that%20the%20kind%20of%20abuse%20they%20apprehended%20--%20this%20power%20will%20not%20be%20misused%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20not%20one%20of%20a%20kind%20situation%2C%26quot%3B%20added%20Justice%20Kaul.%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20seen%20the%20northern%20border%20Punjab%20--%20very%20difficult%20times.%20Similarly%2C%20some%20states%20in%20the%20northeast...%20Tomorrow%20if%20there%20is%20a%20scenario%20that%20each%20of%20these%20states%20face%20this%20problem...%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDoes%20parliament%20have%20the%20power%20to%20convert%20an%20existing%20Indian%20state%20into%20a%20Union%20Territory%3F%26quot%3B%20questioned%20Chief%20Justice%20Chandrachud.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20also%20said%20that%20even%20if%20the%20role%20of%20the%20Constituent%20Assembly%20only%20had%20a%20recommendatory%20role%20regarding%20Article%20370%20--%20which%20gave%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20its%20special%20status%20-%20that%20does%20not%20mean%20it%20can%20be%20overridden%20by%20the%20President%20of%20India.%20In%20an%20earlier%20hearing%2C%20the%20court%20had%20said%20the%20government%20will%20have%20to%20justify%20procedure%20it%20adopted%20to%20scrap%20the%20Article%20370%2C%20as%20it%20could%20not%20assume%20that%20%26quot%3Bend%20justifies%20the%20means%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693374660000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-01%2Fastlnkkg_supreme-cou