nces-second-quarter-2023-unaudited-financial%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecompany%20reported%20second-quarter%3C%2Fa%3E%20revenues%20of%2052.28%20billion%20Chinese%20yuan%2C%20or%20%247.2%20billion%20%E2%80%94%20smashing%20analysts'%20average%20estimates%20of%2043.7%20billion%20yuan%2C%20per%20Refinitiv%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHuang%20was%20worth%20%2432.8%20billion%20as%20of%20August%2030%2C%20per%20Bloomberg%2C%20making%20him%20the%2041st%20richest%20person%20in%20the%20world.%20The%2043-year-old%20has%20seen%20his%20wealth%20soar%20by%2014%25%20this%20year%20thanks%20to%20the%20gains%20in%20PDD%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHuang%20stepped%20down%20as%20the%20company's%20CEO%20in%202020%20and%20as%20chairman%20in%202021%20but%20still%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.marketscreener.com%2Fbusiness-leaders%2FZheng-Huang-5927%2Fbiography%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eretains%20a%2028%25%20stake%20in%20PDD.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EHuang%20came%20out%20of%20an%20early%20retirement%20in%202015%20to%20start%20PDD%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBorn%20in%20the%20eastern%20province%20of%20Zhejiang%2C%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffabulous-life-colin-huang-pinduoduo-2020-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%C2%A0Huang%20worked%20as%20an%20engineer%20and%20project%20manager%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0in%20Google's%20US%20headquarters%20in%202004%20after%20graduating%20with%20a%20master's%20degree%20in%20computer%20science%20from%20the%20University%20of%20Wisconsin.%20He%20returned%20to%20China%20in%202006%20and%20was%20part%20of%20the%20founding%20team%20of%20Google%20China.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHuang%20founded%20his%20first%20company%20%E2%80%94%20the%20e-commerce%20site%20Ouku.com%20%E2%80%94%20in%202007%20and%20sold%20it%20in%202010%20before%20starting%20Leqi%2C%20an%C2%A0e-commerce%20marketing%20firm.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20he%20decided%20to%20retire%20in%20%3Ca%20href