der%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F103191508.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EFrom%20Ranveer%20Singh%20and%20Priyanka%20Chopra%20to%20Kiara%20Knightley%20and%20Matthew%20Macfadyen%2C%20Shah%20Rukh%20Khan%20and%20Aishwarya%20Rai%20Bachchan%20here's%20a%20list%20of%20actors%20who%20have%20pallied%20up%20as%20siblings%20and%20also%20scorched%20up%20the%20screens%20as%20lovers.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fenglish%2Factors-who-have-played-siblings-and-lovers-on-screen%2Fphotostory%2F103191508.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22R%20Ashwin%20Hits%20Bullseye%20As%20He%20Digs%20Out%20Secret%20To%20Pakistan%20Team's%20Rise%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20Asia%20Cup%202023%20begins%2C%20it's%20the%20India%20and%20Pakistan%20teams%20that%20are%20being%20considered%20the%20'favourites'%20for%20the%20title.%20Though%20it%20was%20the%20Sri%20Lankan%20team%20that%20won%20the%20title%20last%20time%20around%20(in%20the%20T20%20version%20of%20the%20tournament)%2C%20India%20and%20Pakistan%20are%20being%20seen%20as%20the%20two%20outright%20favourites.%20While%20the%20Indian%20team%20has%20won%20the%20tournament%2C%20in%20the%20ODI%20version%2C%20the%20most%20number%20of%20times%2C%20Pakistan%20have%20really%20pulled%20their%20socks%20up%20in%20the%20last%20few%20years.%20Veteran%20Indian%20spinner%2C%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Ravichandran%20Ashwin%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1109-ravichandran-ashwin-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERavichandran%20Ashwin%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20in%20his%20preview%20for%20the%20Asia%20Cup%202023%2C%20tried%20to%20decode%20the%20rise%20of%20the%20Paksitan%20team%20over%20the%20last%205-6%20years%2C%20and%20what%20makes%20them%20favourites%20this%20year%2C%20alongside%20the%20Indian%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20used%20to%20envy%20looking%20at%20the%20Pakistan%20side.%205-6%20years%20back%2C%20they%20used%20to%20struggle%20in%20big%20tournaments%20like%20Asia%20Cup%20and%20World%20Cup.%20Yes%2C%20of%20course%2C%20they%20have%20won%20big%20tournaments%20in%20the%20past.%20They%20have%20won%20the%201992%20World%20Cup%20and%20delivered%20a%20consistent%20performance%20in%20the%20T20%20World%20Cup.%20The%20main%20reason%20for%20the%20last%205-6%20years'%20rise%20can%20be%20attributed%20to%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Babar%20Azam%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F59905-mohammad-babar-azam-playerprofile%5C%22%3EBabar%20Azam%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20Mohammad%20Rizwan%2C%26quot%3B%20Ashwin%20said%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DHjCkmyUMMbE%5C%22%3Evideo%20on%20his%20YouTube%20channel%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20Ashwin%20also%20credited%20Pakistani%20players'%20experience%20of%20playing%20in%20different%20conditions%20all%20across%20the%20globe%20as%20a%20major%20reason%20behind%20their%20improved%20ability%20to%20deliver%20on%20big%20stages.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20all%20comes%20down%20to%20their%20squad%20depth.%20Pakistan%20have%20always%20produced%20extraordinary%20cricketers.%20because%20of%20tape%20ball%20cricket%2C%20they%20have%20always%20had%20fast%20bowlers%20coming%20through%20their%20ranks.%20Their%20batting%20has%20been%20special%20in%20the%20late%2090s%20and%202000s.%20But%20their%20exposure%20to%20different%20leagues%20has%20been%20a%20major%20reason%20for%20their%20re-emergence%20in%20the%20last%205-6%20years.%20They%20have%20PSL.%20In%20the%20recent%20BBL%20drafts%20they%20were%20at%20least%2060-70%20Pakistan%20players.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20are%20playing%20Test%20cricket%20and%20play%20their%20own%20T20%20leagues.%20But%20they%20are%20also%20playing%20all%20around%20the%20world%20in%20England%20and%20Australia%2C%20and%20this%20year%20there%20aren't%20many%20Pakistan%20players%20in%20CPL%2C%20but%20they%20always%20dominate%20CPL%20too.%20They%20play%20in%20the%20Emirati%20League%2C%20USA%2C%20and%20also%20in%20Canada.%20When%20talent%20meets%20opportunity%20with%20different%20exposures.%20In%20IPL%2C%20we%20make%20sure%20that%20talent%20meets%20opportunity%20and%20that's%20why%20we%20are%20seeing%20more%20cricketers%20from%20different%20regions%2C%26quot%3B%20Ashwin%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat's%20why%20in%20the%20last%205-6%20years%2C%20Pakistan%20are%20not%20only%20producing%20world-class%20cricketers%20but%20these%20talents%20are%20only%20delivering%20in%20the%20big%20stages.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAshwin%20feels%20if%20Babar%20Azam%20and%20Mohamad%20Rizwan%20remain%20on%20song%20in%20the%20coming%20months%2C%20it%20would%20be%20tough%20to%20be%20Pakistan%20in%20the%20Asia%20Cup%20and%20the%20ODI%20World%20Cup.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20Babar%20Azam%20and%20Mohammad%20Rizwan%20gives%20consistent%20performances%20with%20the%20bat%20in%20the%20middle-order%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3Ethen%20Pakistan%20are%20going%20to%20be%20one%20hell%20of%20a%20team%20going%20into%20this%20Asia%20Cup%20and%20World%20Cup.%20It%20will%20take%20some%20beating.%20Pakistan%20is%20an%20exceptional%20side.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20year's%20Asia%20Cup's%20most%20games%20will%20be%20played%20in%20Sri%20Lanka.%20Who%20else%20are%20more%20equipped%20for%20Sri%20Lankan%20conditions%20than%20Pakistan%3F%20Because%20almost%20all%20the%20foreigners%20in%20the%20Lanka%20Premier%20League%20are%20Pakistanis%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20asserted.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693369500000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2F7glj0td8_r-ashwin-youtube_625x300_30_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fasia-cup-2023%2Fif-babar-and-rizwan-fire-r-ashwin-fires-firm-warning-to-india-other-asia-cup-sides-4341163%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Rav