it%20that%20roiled%20the%20first%20family%20of%20corporate%20India.%20More%20than%20a%20decade%20ago%20Reliance's%20founder%2C%20Dhirubhai%20Ambani%2C%20died%20without%20a%20will%20or%20a%20clear%20leadership%20transition%2C%20stirring%20a%20bitter%20feud%20between%20Mukesh%20and%20his%20younger%20brother%2C%20Anil.%20Reliance%20was%20eventually%20divided%20up%20following%20the%20intervention%20of%20their%20mother.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThree%20years%20ago%2C%20Ambani%20began%20including%20his%20children%20in%20major%20family%20businesses%20decisions%2C%20involving%20them%20in%20talks%20with%20Meta%20Platforms%20Inc.%20to%20secure%20a%20%245.7%20billion%20investment.%20Formal%20roles%20have%20also%20been%20carved%20out%20for%20Isha%2C%20Akash%20and%20Anant%20in%20Reliance's%20energy%2C%20retail%2C%20telecom%20and%20digital%20services%20arms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEach%20child%20owns%20a%20%24236%20million%20direct%20ownership%20stake%20in%20Reliance%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Bloomberg%20Billionaires%20Index.%20But%20it%20remains%20to%20be%20seen%20whether%20Ambani's%20children%20can%20emulate%20their%20father's%20success%20turning%20the%20oil-to-consumer%20titan%20into%20India's%20biggest%20company%20by%20market%20value%20as%20the%20conglomerate%20increasingly%20attempts%20to%20reposition%20itself%20for%20the%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHere's%20what%20we%20know%20about%20the%20next%20generation%20trio%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIsha%20Ambani%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20an%20MBA%20from%20Stanford%20University%20and%20experience%20working%20at%20McKinsey%20%26amp%3B%20Co.%2C%20Ambani's%2031-year-old%20daughter%20Isha%20leads%20the%20conglomerate's%20retail%20business%2C%20driving%20its%20expansion%20and%20the%20acquisition%20of%20brands%2C%20including%20the%20once%20largely%20defunct%20and%20nostalgia-tinged%20Campa%20Cola%20soda%20brand%20that%20was%20the%20market%20leader%20in%20India's%20socialist%20era.%3C%2Fp%3