about%20him%20whenever%20he%20is%20at%20home).%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20part%20of%20Ashraf's%20preparations%20also%20included%20watching%20Neeraj%20Chopra's%20videos.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20he%20was%20at%20home%20during%20the%20injury%2C%20he%20would%20talk%20about%20javelin%20and%20the%20similarities%20between%20tent%20pegging%20and%20javelin.%20He%20would%20tell%20us%20that%20it's%20as%20precise%20as%20tent%20pegging%20and%20the%20right%20angle%20and%20velocity%20have%20to%20be%20achieved%20in%20javelin%20too.%20He%20would%20often%20watch%20YouTube%20videos%20and%20we%20would%20see%20the%20Indian%20boy%20on%20his%20mobile%20phone%2C%26quot%3B%20Ashraf%20further%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThings%20weren't%20always%20the%20most%20comfortable%20for%20Arshad%20and%20his%20family%2C%20with%20the%20athlete%20barely%20managing%20to%20make%20ends%20meet%20with%20his%20earnings.%20His%20uncle%20revealed%20that%20he%20took%20care%20of%20Arshad's%20diet%20by%20always%20giving%20him%20milk%20and%20ghee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20seen%20days%20when%20I%20would%20earn%20300-400%20rupees%20a%20day%20and%20I%20had%20to%20support%20nine%20beings%20at%20home.%20But%20we%20made%20sure%20that%20Arshad%20and%20his%20siblings%20got%20milk%20and%20ghee.%20Even%20now%2C%20when%20he%20returns%20to%20the%20village%20after%20winning%20a%20Worlds%20medal%2C%20he%20will%20ask%20for%20a%20glass%20of%20milk%20and%20dishes%20made%20of%20desi%20ghee%2C%26quot%3B%20Ashraf%20revealed.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693364760000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2F0fdl8ggo_neeraj-and-arshad_625x300_28_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fathletics%2Fneeraj-chopras-videos-ghee-and-milk-diet-arshad-nadeems-uncle-on-pakistan-athletes-rise-4338026%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Arshad%20Nadeem%20finished%20second%2C%20behind%20Neeraj%20Chopra%2C%20in%20the%20Men's%20Javelin%20Throw%20final%20at%20the%20Wor