the%20town%20of%20Shebekino%2C%20Belgorod%20Region%2C%20Russia%20on%20June%2021%2C%202023.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64eead8226dda200194d8154%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223648%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBroken%20windows%20of%20a%20damaged%20residential%20building%20is%20seen%20after%20shelling%20by%20the%20Ukrainian%20Armed%20Forces%20in%20the%20town%20of%20Shebekino%2C%20Belgorod%20Region%2C%20Russia%20on%20June%2021%2C%202023.%3Cp%3EStringer%2FAnadolu%20Agency%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EA%20senior%20Russian%20police%20officer%20was%20killed%20by%20a%20drone%20while%20mowing%20his%20lawn%20on%20Saturday%2C%20reports%20say.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIdentified%20as%20Alexey%20Ch.%2C%20the%20man%20worked%20in%20Russia's%20anti-corruption%20service%2C%20Baza%20reported.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20local%20governor%20confirmed%20a%20man%20was%20killed%20by%20a%20drone%20while%20mowing%20grass%20at%20a%20country%20house.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EA%20lieutenant%20colonel%20in%20the%20Russian%20police%20was%20killed%20on%20Saturday%20by%20a%20drone%20attack%20while%20mowing%20the%20lawn%20at%20his%20country%20house%2C%20according%20to%20local%20news%20reports.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20senior%20officer%2C%20identified%20as%20Alexey%20Ch.%2C%20was%20the%20deputy%20head%20of%20a%20regional%20department%20in%20Russia's%20anti-corruption%20and%20economic%20security%20service%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fbazabazon%2F20883%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERussian%20Telegram%20channel%20Baza%20reported.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20on%20his%20day%20off%20and%20mowing%20grass%20in%20Shchetinovka%2C%20a%20rural%20locality%20in%20Belgorod%2C%20when%20the%20drone%20attack%20struck%2C%20per%20Baza.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVyacheslav%20Gladkov%2C%20the%20governor%20of%20Belgorod%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2