26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222117%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20progress%20photo%20of%20a%20cob%20house%20being%20built.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64dec971bd98a6001978b3fa%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221588%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20progress%20photo%20of%20a%20cob%20house%20being%20built.%3Cp%3EDaniel%20Ray%2FSpiritwood%20Natural%20Building%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20participants%20who%20attend%20the%20couple's%20workshops%20come%20from%20the%20area%20as%20well%20as%20far-flung%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20recently%20had%20someone%20from%20as%20far%20as%20Alaska%20come%20to%20our%20classes%2C%26quot%3B%20Daniel%20said.%20%26quot%3BShe%20wasn't%20sure%20what%20to%20expect%2C%20but%20after%20nine%20days%20and%20being%20able%20to%20build%20a%20small%20house%2C%20she%20was%20determined%20to%20go%20home%20and%20begin%20her%20own%20house.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223984%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20woman%20working%20on%20laying%20the%20interior%20floors%20of%20a%20cob%20house.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64ed50e615cc5d00198cad44%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222988%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20woman%20working%20on%20laying%20the%20interior%20floors%20of%20a%20cob%20house.%3Cp%3EDaniel%20Ray%2FSpiritwood%20Natural%20Building%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3EEducating%20others%20on%20the%20benefits%20of%20living%20in%20a%20cob%20house%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20teaching%20workshop%20participants%20practical%20skills%2C%20the%20couple%20is%20also%20passionate%20about%20educating%20others%20about%20the%20benefits%20of%20living%20in%20an%20earthen%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20instance%2C%20the%20interiors%20of%20cob%20houses%20are%20much%20cooler%20than%20typical%20houses%20during%20summer%2C%20which%20translates%20into%20cost-savings%20in%20