d%20a%20series%20of%20negotiations%20to%20craft%20the%20final%20debt-relief%20plan.%20Last%20month%2C%20the%20department%20held%20its%20public%20hearing%20%E2%80%94%20and%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20it%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ed.gov%2Fnews%2Fpress-releases%2Fbiden-harris-administration-seeks-nominations-non-federal-negotiators-continue-rulemaking-process-student-debt-relief%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eannounced%3C%2Fa%3E%20it%20is%20seeking%20nominations%20for%20non-federal%20negotiators%20to%20participate%20in%20the%20negotiating%20sessions%20beginning%20in%20October.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20ruled%20against%20the%20Biden-Harris%20Administration's%20student%20debt%20relief%20plan%2C%20we%20did%20not%20waste%20a%20moment%20opening%20up%20a%20new%20pathway%20to%20debt%20relief%2C%26quot%3B%20Education%20Secretary%20Miguel%20Cardona%20said%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ed.gov%2Fnews%2Fpress-releases%2Fbiden-harris-administration-seeks-nominations-non-federal-negotiators-continue-rulemaking-process-student-debt-relief%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estatement%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20we%20pursue%20debt%20relief%20through%20this%20process%2C%20one%20of%20the%20most%20important%20steps%20is%20bringing%20together%20diverse%20perspectives%20to%20help%20us%20craft%20the%20strongest%20possible%20regulations%20for%20borrowers%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20continued.%20%26quot%3BThe%20Student%20Loan%20Relief%20committee%20will%20include%20students%2C%20borrowers%2C%20state%20officials%2C%20civil%20rights%20advocates%2C%20representatives%20from%20colleges%20and%20universities%2C%20and%20other%20stakeholders%20so%20we%20can%20make%20sure%20all%20voices%20are%20heard%20and%20the%20needs%20of%20borrowers%20are%20fully%20considered.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20press%20release%2C%20negotiations%20will%20be%20held%20vir