%2Ftwitter.com%2Felonmusk%2Fstatus%2F1694403816920137880%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EAugust%2023%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EImperfections%20in%20the%20doors%20and%20other%20panels%20make%20the%20vehicle%20look%20like%20a%20rolling%20funhouse%20mirror%20%E2%80%94%20not%20exactly%20the%20uniform%2C%20space-age%20truck%20that%20was%20promised.%20The%20effect%20was%20more%20pronounced%20in%20earlier%20Cybertruck%20photos%2C%20but%20it's%20still%20noticeable%20here%2C%20just%20weeks%20away%20from%20customer%20deliveries.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20are%20going%20to%20see%20funny%20reflections%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20finished%20product%2C%20Wardle%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20side%20of%20the%20truck%20looks%20less%20like%20a%20cohesive%20design%20and%20more%20like%20%26quot%3Bfour%20flat%20panels%20that%20happen%20to%20be%20adjacent%20to%20each%20other.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20potential%20issue%20he%20foresees%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-cybertruck-might-be-fingerprint-magnet-stainless-steel-body-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efingerprints%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnyone%20who's%20owned%20a%20stainless%20steel%20fridge%20knows%20they%20are%20a%20magnet%20for%20grime%20and%20are%20a%20nightmare%20to%20keep%20clean.%20Now%20imagine%20that%20issue%20on%20practically%20every%20surface%20of%20your%20truck%2C%20which%20is%20routinely%20exposed%20to%20nasty%20environments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20isn't%20sure%20any%20of%20it%20will%20matter%20to%20the%20Cybertruck's%20most%20enthusiastic%20fans.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMaybe%20customers%20are%20going%20to%20like%20them%20to%20get%20all%20grubby%20and%20dirty%20and%20have%20that%20sort%20of%20'Star%20Wars'%20look%20about%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20for%20more%20traditional%20folks%2C%20they%20might%20be%20bothered%20about%20paying%20probably%20a%20lot%20of%20money%20for%20this%20car%20and%20fin