E%20Fresh%20violence%20broke%20out%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20August%2029%2C%20in%20the%20adjoining%20villages%20of%20Naransena%20in%20Manipur%2C%20claiming%20the%20lives%20of%20three%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20them%20belonged%20to%20the%20Kuki-Zo%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20victim%2C%20identified%20as%20Jangminlun%20Gangte%2C%20aged%2030%2C%20was%20shot%20in%20the%20Khoirentak%20area%20of%20Churachandpur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Francis%2C%20Jangminlun%E2%80%99s%20cousin%2C%20alleged%2C%20%E2%80%9CHe%20was%20killed%20by%20the%20Manipur%20police%20commandos%20during%20their%20attack%20on%20our%20village%2C%20Khousabung.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKhousabung%20is%20only%205%20kilometres%20away%20from%20Naransena.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJangminlun%20had%20been%20on%20duty%20since%20May%2015%2C%20overseeing%20local%20volunteers%20on%20the%20frontline.%20According%20to%20the%20ITLF%2C%20intense%20gunfire%20broke%20out%20when%20village%20volunteers%20retaliated%2C%20leading%20to%20his%20death.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrancis%20had%20spoken%20with%20Jangminlun%2C%20before%20he%20headed%20to%20the%20frontline.%20During%20the%20conversation%2C%20he%20had%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CTake%20care%20of%20my%20family%20in%20case%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20make%20it%2C%20and%20please%20don%E2%80%99t%20cry%20because%20I%E2%80%99m%20sacrificing%20today%20for%20a%20better%20tomorrow.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOut%20of%20the%20other%20two%20people%20who%20died%20in%20the%20firing%20incident%2C%20one%20of%20them%20has%20been%20identified%20as%20Laibunjam%20Inao%20(27).%20He%20was%20shot%20in%20the%20head.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20local%20reports%2C%20he%20was%20taken%20to%20Raj%20Medicity%2C%20but%20died%20on%20the%20way%20to%20the%20hospital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20press%20statement%20issued%20by%20the%20Manipur%20Police%20Control%20Room%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9COn%2029.08.2023%2C%20a%20firing%20incident%20occurred%20between%20armed%20miscreants%20in%20the%20adjoining%20villages%20of%20Naransena%2C%20resulting%20in%2002%20fatalities%20and%2007%20individuals%20sustaining%20bullet%20or%20splinter%20injuries.%20District%20Police%2C%20AR%2C%20Army%2C%20and%20CAPF%20forces%20deployed%20in%20the%20area%20promptly%20responded%20and%20managed%20to%20bring%20the%20situation%20under%20control.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJust%20ten%20days%20ago%2C%20three%20individuals%20lost%20their%20lives%20in%20the%20Kuki%20village%20of%20Thowai%20Kuki.%20The%20victims%20were%20identified%20as%20Thangkhokai%20Haokip%20(35)%2C%20Jamkhogin%20Haokip%20(26)%2C%20and%20Hollenson%20Baite%20(24).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20ongoing%20violence%20in%20Manipur%2C%20over%20150%20people%20have%20died%2C%20and%20less%20than%20half%20of%20the%20deceased%E2%80%99s%20families%20have%20received%20a%20compensation%20of%20Rs%205%20lakh%20as%20against%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fkin-of-manipur-violence-victims-to-get-rs-10-lakh-relief-8637717%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DThe%2520government%2520on%2520Tuesday%2520announced%2Cstate%2520to%2520review%2520the%2520situation.%5C%22%3Epromised%3C%2Fa%3E%20Rs%2010%20lakh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJangminlun%E2%80%99s%20family%20has%20not%20yet%20registered%20a%20first%20information%20report%20(FIR)%2C%20till%20the%20time%20of%20going%20to%20press.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20in%20the%20Churachandpur%20district%2C%204%2C036%20zero%20FIRs%20have%20been%20registered%2C%20including%2012%20crimes%20against%20women%20%E2%80%93%20six%20each%20at%20the%20Churachandpur%20police%20station%20and%20women%E2%80%99s%20police%20station.%20Furthermore%2C%201%2C283%20regular%20FIRs%20have%20been%20registered%2C%20and%201%2C622%20FIRs%20originally%20filed%20in%20other%20districts%20have%20been%20converted%20into%20regular%20FIRs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20this%20incident%20transpired%20on%20the%20same%20day%20as%20the%20Manipur%20government%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fmanipur-assembly-monsoon-session-anusuiya-uikey%5C%22%3Efirst%20assembly%20session%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20during%20which%20three%20resolutions%20were%20passed%20in%20the%20House%2C%20according%20to%20information%20provided%20by%20the%20governor%E2%80%99s%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20resolutions%20included%20a%20commitment%20to%20maintaining%20harmony%20without%20discrimination%2C%20an%20aspiration%20for%20peace%20through%20dialogue%2C%20and%20an%20appeal%20to%20renounce%20violence.%20Opposition%20MLAs%20from%20the%20Congress%20party%20demanded%20a%20two-minute%20silence%20in%20honour%20of%20those%20killed%20in%20the%20violence%20and%20sought%20an%20extension%20of%20the%20single-day%20session%20to%20five%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Speaker%20Thokchom%20Satyabrata%20Singh%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fmanipur-assemblys-one-day-session-adjourned-after-11-minutes%5C%22%3Eadjourned%20the%20session%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%2011%20minutes.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693332690000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fmanipur-fresh-violence-erupts-in-churachandpur-one-person-from-the-kuki-zo-community-dies%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ten%20days%20ago%2C%20three%20individuals%20lost%20their%20lives%20in%20the%20Kuki%20village%20of%20Thowai%20Kuki.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Rare%20blue%20supermoon%20could%20worsen%20life-threatening%20floods%20triggered%20by%20Florida%20hurricane%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693332660000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F23%2F08%2F70x70%2Fskynews-idalia-storm-idalia_6266547.jpg%3F20230829115649%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fhurricane-idalia-state-of-emergency-de