rk%20soon.%20%E2%80%9CHe%20would%20often%20despairingly%20say%2C%20%E2%80%98I%20will%20have%20to%20kill%20myself%20if%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20get%20my%20job%20back.%E2%80%99%20He%20was%20always%20worried%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Rinku.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Sunday%20evening%20(August%2027)%2C%20Mohit%20left%20the%20house%2C%20saying%20that%20he%20was%20on%20his%20way%20to%20Bareilly%20in%20the%20hope%20of%20getting%20back%20his%20job.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20thought%20he%20was%20on%20his%20way%20to%20the%20Bareilly%20depot.%20But%20it%20seems%20he%20changed%20his%20plan.%20We%20later%20received%20a%20phone%20call%20informing%20us%20that%20he%20had%20died%20after%20coming%20under%20a%20train%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Rinku.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMohit%20worked%20as%20a%20contractual%20employee%20with%20the%20UP%20State%20Road%20Transport%20Corporation%20(UPSRTC)%20and%20earned%20a%20monthly%20salary%20of%20Rs%2017%2C000.%20He%2C%20along%20with%20his%20three%20brothers%2C%20shared%2010%20bighas%20of%20land.%20The%20earnings%20from%20the%20cultivation%20and%20two%20buffaloes%20along%20with%20Mohit%E2%80%99s%20salary%20kept%20the%20family%20going.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20family%20consists%20of%20three%20brothers%2C%20their%20parents%2C%20sister%2C%20and%20the%20wives%20of%20Mohit%20and%20Rinku.%20Mohit%20left%20behind%20a%20four-year-old%20son.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20job%20loss%20caused%20him%20financial%20and%20mental%20stress%2C%20said%20his%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMohit%20and%20Krishna%20Pal%20Singh%2C%20the%20driver%20of%20the%20Delhi-bound%20UPSRTC%20bus%2C%20were%20suspended%20and%20later%20terminated%20in%20June%20after%20a%20passenger%20on%20the%20bus%20shot%20a%20video%20of%20the%20two%20Muslim%20men%20offering%20namaz%20and%20shared%20it%20online.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-width%3D%5C%22550%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%20data-dnt%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EOn%20June%203rd%2C%20People%20shot%20video%20of%20two%20passengers%20offering%20Namaz%2C%20questioned%20the%20Driver%20and%20conductor%20for%20stopping%20the%20bus.%20One%20of%20the%20passengers%20complaints%20against%20both%20for%20stopping%20the%20bus.%20Both%20Driver%20%26amp%3B%20Conductor%20Mohit%20Yadav%20were%20suspended.%2027th%2C%20Aug.%20%F0%9F%91%87%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F8pSPzPU1oj%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2F8pSPzPU1oj%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F8RlMDgrvxQ%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F8RlMDgrvxQ%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Mohammed%20Zubair%20(%40zoo_bear)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fzoo_bear%2Fstatus%2F1696391683070738478%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EAugust%2029%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20video%20statement%2C%20after%20his%20termination%2C%20Mohit%20had%20clarified%20that%20he%20did%20not%20stop%20the%20bus%20specifically%20for%20the%20two%20Muslim%20men%20to%20offer%20namaz.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bus%20was%20halted%20after%20three%20passengers%20had%20approached%20him%2C%20requesting%20that%20the%20bus%20be%20stopped%20so%20that%20they%20could%20urinate.%20Since%20the%20two%20Muslim%20passengers%20had%20already%20requested%20Yadav%20to%20allow%20them%20to%20offer%20namaz%2C%20he%20had%20asked%20them%20to%20make%20use%20of%20the%20halt%20and%20offer%20namaz.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20didn%E2%80%99t%20stop%20the%20bus%20for%20the%20namaz.%20By%20the%20time%20those%20who%20wanted%20to%20relieve%20themselves%20returned%2C%20the%20two%20had%20already%20concluded%20their%20namaz.%20The%20bus%20must%20have%20stopped%20for%20just%20two%20minutes%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20he%20allegedly%20died%20by%20suicide%2C%20his%20widow%2C%20Rinki%20Yadav%2C%20told%20local%20media%20that%20her%20husband%20had%20been%20unjustly%20terminated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHe%20did%20not%20do%20anything%20wrong%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said%2C%20repeating%20what%20her%20husband%20had%20earlier%20said%20in%20his%20defence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHe%20didn%E2%80%99t%20stop%20the%20bus%20for%20the%20namaz%20but%20for%20those%20who%20wanted%20to%20urinate.%20They%20%5Bthose%20who%20read%20namaz%5D%20prayed%20for%20only%20two%20minutes.%20That%E2%80%99s%20all%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20family%20is%20yet%20to%20lodge%20a%20police%20complaint%2C%20Rinku%20said%20the%20assistant%20regional%20manager%20(Bareilly)%20of%20the%20UPSRTC%2C%C2%A0who%20sacked%20him%2C%20was%20to%20be%20blamed%20for%20his%20brother%E2%80%99s%20death.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20losing%20his%20job%2C%20Mohit%20tried%20to%20get%20it%20back.%20He%20met%20with%20the%20concerned%20official%2C%20but%20despite%20assurances%2C%20he%20did%20not%20succeed%20in%20getting%20his%20job%20back.%20%E2%80%9CJust%20three%20days%20ago%2C%20he%20had%20gone%20to%20meet%20with%20the%20assistant%20regional%20manager%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Rinku.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMohit%20did%20not%20leave%20behind%20any%20note.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20police%20is%20yet%20to%20make%20a%20detailed%20statement%20on%20the%20matter%2C%20the%20main%20opposition%20Samajwadi%20Party%20said%20it%20would%20provide%20Yadav%E2%80%99s%20family%20a%20sum%20of%20Rs%202%20lakh%20in%20support.%20The%20party%20demanded%20that%20the%20Yogi%20Adityanath%20government%20compensate%20Yadav%E2%80%99s%20family%20with%20Rs%2050%20lakh%20and%20a%20government%20job%20to%20one%20of%20his%20family%20members.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESP%20president%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20criticised%20the%20state%20government%20for%20terminating%20Yadav%E2%80%99s%20job%20due%20to%20the%20act%20of%20allowing%20some%20passengers%20to%20offer%20prayers%20for%20two%20minutes.%20He%20described%20the%20episode%20as%20%E2%80%9Cunfortunate%2C%20condemnable%20and%20shameful%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEvery%20employee%20of%20the%20UP%20transport%20department%20should%20d