me-in-five-years-12950308%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fmps-call-for-unclassified-strategy-on-china-as-foreign-secretary-james-clevery-visits-for-first-time-in-five-years-12950308%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fmps-call-for-unclassified-strategy-on-china-as-foreign-secretary-james-clevery-visits-for-first-time-in-five-years-12950308%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Delhi%20HC%20Dismisses%20PIL%20Seeking%20Disclosure%20of%20EVM%20Serial%20Numbers%20and%20Manufacturers%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F06%2F02121850%2Fdelhi-high-court-1558979556.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20Delhi%20high%20court%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20August%2029%2C%20dismissed%20a%20public%20interest%20litigation%20(PIL)%20seeking%20disclosure%20of%20electronic%20voting%20machine%20(EVM)%20serial%20numbers%20and%20manufacturers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20plea%20requested%20that%20these%20details%20should%20be%20provided%20to%20the%20representatives%20of%20the%20political%20parties%20before%20the%20first-level%20checking%20(FLC)%20is%20completed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAhead%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20the%20FLC%20of%20the%20machines%20is%20the%20first%20step%20of%20the%20verification%20process.%20However%2C%20the%20petition%20raised%20doubts%20over%20the%20credibility%20of%20the%20verification%20process.%20It%20pointed%20out%20that%20the%20FLC%20was%20completed%20even%20though%20the%20Congress%20party%20boycotted%20the%20process%2C%20saying%20that%20they%20were%20not%20provided%20with%20any%20information.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20the%20FLC%20is%20over%2C%20the%20machines%20are%20sealed%20and%20stored%20in%20designated%20warehouses%20and%20opened%20only%20when%20the%20poll%20process%20begins%2C%20starting%20with%20the%20notification%20of%20the%20polls.%20The%20FLC%20for%20Delhi%20has%20been%20completed%2C%20the%20counsel%20for%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20told%20the%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20petition%20was%20filed%20by%20Delhi%20Pradesh%20Congress%20Committee%20chief%2C%20Anil%20Choudhary.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20these%20crucial%20details%2C%20what%20is%20the%20point%20of%20simply%20going%20to%20look%20at%20the%20machines%3F%20All%20machines%20look%20the%20same.%20In%20order%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20the%20serial%20number%20of%20the%20machine%20matches%20with%20our%20list%2C%20they%20have%20to%20provide%20%5Bus%20with%5D%20the%20serial%20numbers%2C%20model%2C%20manufacturer.%20They%20are%20refusing%20to%20give%20us%20information%20about%20the%20basic%20hardware%20that%20will%20be%20used%20in%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%E2%80%9D%20one%20of%20the%20counsels%20for%20the%20petitioner%20told%20the%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20petition%20says%20that%20letters%20were%20sent%2C%20inviting%20representatives%20of%20various%20political%20parties%20for%20the%20preparatory%20meetings.%20These%20meetings%20were%20scheduled%20to%20be%20held%20between%20July%206%20and%2012.%20These%20letters%20were%20issued%20by%20various%20%3Cspan%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ESub-Divisional%20Magistrates%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%20who%20are%20authorised%20to%20conduct%20the%20FLC.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20letter%20said%20that%20the%20EVM%20and%20the%20voter%20verifiable%20paper%20audit%20trails%20(VVPATs)%20would%20be%20checked%20at%20the%20respective%20district%20headquarters%20in%20different%20parts%20of%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20rather%20than%20addressing%20the%20concerns%20raised%20by%20the%20party%2C%20the%20Chief%20Electoral%20Officer%2C%20Delhi%2C%20went%20ahead%20with%20finalising%20the%20dates%20for%20the%20FLC%20which%20was%20to%20be%20conducted%20from%20July%2015%20to%20July%2030.%20And%20since%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20concerns%20were%20not%20addressed%2C%20the%20Congress%20boycotted%20the%20FLC%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20SDMs%20issued%20letters%20to%20the%20Congress%20party%2C%20requesting%20them%20to%20participate.%20But%20they%20didn%E2%80%99t.%20And%20the%20FLC%20continued%20without%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20FLC%20has%20been%20completed%20for%20Delhi%2C%20Kerala%2C%20and%20Jharkhand%2C%20and%20is%20underway%20in%20five%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20petitioner%20filed%20a%20representation%20before%20the%20Chief%20Electoral%20Officer%2C%20saying%20that%20without%20this%20information%2C%20they%20will%20be%20unable%20to%20train%20their%20officers.%20These%20officers%20would%20be%20involved%20in%20the%20election%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chief%20Electoral%20Officer%2C%20Ranbir%20Singh%2C%20heard%20the%20representatives%3B%20however%2C%20he%20did%20not%20address%20any%20of%20the%20issues%20raised%20by%20the%20party%20leaders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20entire%20attempt%20of%20the%20Election%20Commission%20is%20highly%20surreptitious.%20The%20procedure%20followed%20for%20the%20commencement%20of%20the%20FLC%20was%20not%20transparent%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20the%20PIL.%20Only%20oral%20assurances%20were%20made%20by%20the%20officers%20concerned.%20The%20Chief%20Electoral%20Officer%20rejected%20the%20contentions%20of%20the%20Congress%20in%20a%20written%20reply%20on%20August%2010%2C%20forcing%20the%20petitioner%20to%20move%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20petitioner%20also%20pointed%20out%2C%20citing%20circulars%20of%202017%20and%202022%2C%20that%20for%20the%20elections%20held%20in%20the%20past%2C%20the%20FLC%20process%20had%20started%20six%20months%20in%20advance%2C%20as%20per%20ECI%E2%80%99s%20instructions.%20However%2C%20this%20time%20the%20process%20has%20been%20advanced%20by%20three%20months%2C%20arbitrarily%2C%20by%20the%20Chief%20Electoral%20Officer%2C%20making%20the%20%E2%80%9Cstakeholder%20political%20parties%20a%20silent%20spectator%20to%20the%20entire%20process%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20counsel%20for%20the%20Election%20Commission%20told%20the%20court%20that%20the%20FLC%20process%20is%20being%20conducted%20as%20per%20the%20election%20manual%2C%20which%20has%20not%20been%20challenged%20by%20the%20petitioners.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20manual%20says%20that%20after%20the%20%5Bfirst-level%5D%20checking%20is%20done%2C%20the%20machine%20is%20sealed%20in%20the%20presence%20of%20the%20representatives%20and%20details%20are%20provided%20after%20that.%20If%20the%20details%20are%20to%20be%20provided%20before%20the%20FLC%2C%20then%20it%20will%20be%20a%20cumbersome%20exercise%20and%20the%20FLC%20across%20the%20country%20will%20have%20to%20start%20afresh.%20This%20is%20not%20a%20minor%20exercise%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJagdeep%20Chokar%20from%20the%20Association%20for%20Democratic%20reforms%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20FLC%20is%20the%20first%20step%20in%20the%20process%20of%20electronic%20voting.%20The%20entire%20process%20has%20to%20be%20and%20should%20be%20transparent%20and%20open%20to%20scrutiny.%20It%20is%20imperative%20that%20the%20outcome%20of%20the%20FLC%20be%20shared%2C%20otherwise%20the%20curtain%20of%20opacity%20will%20continue%20to%20hide%20the%20functioning%20of%20the%20EVMs.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20reasoned%20court%20order%20is%20expected%20to%20be%20uploaded%20soon.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693324304000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F06%2F02121850%2Fdelhi-high-court-1558979556.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fdelhi-hc-dismisses-pil-seeking-disclosure-of-evm-serial-numbers-and-manufacturers%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20plea%20requested%20that%20these%20details%20should%20be%20provided%20to%20the%20representatives%20of%20the%20political%20parties%20before%20the%20first-level%20checking%20is%20completed.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A6%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22ht